### Diary entry endpoints

### Get all entries
GET {{apiurl}}/entries

### Get entry by id //alempana laitetaan entry ja voi hakea viimeisimmällä tästä entrin
GET {{apiurl}}/entries/7

### post new entry
POST {{apiurl}}/entries
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "user_id": 3,
  "entry_date": "2026-02-05",
  "mood": "Kipeä",
  "weight": 101,
  "sleep_hours": 7,
  "notes": "testikirjaus"

}

